Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The property is situated mid-block along the south side Main Street (Rt 40), which is the main commercial corridor in the Atlantic County Seat, Mays Landing, NJ. The property is located directly across the street from the county complex which houses the surrogate clerk and other county offices.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Former Government Office with County Seat Location

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: American Metro Center, a 487,087 SF office building in Hamilton, New Jersey, is a transit oriented, retro office campus situated in the Princeton/Route 1 submarket. Built in the late 1800's, the American Metro Center of today is the end result of a dynamic transformation of the original home of the American Standard manufacturing facility into a Class A, state of the art, office campus. The restored complex affords tenants a uniquely high character and flexible office environment with open floor plans within an industrial chic setting.
